message.body: I can take the college shuttle to Brynmawr campus and walk to the town. Unfortunately there is no nice place on the campus. Do you know of a pleasant cafe in Bryn Mawr? Otherwise I can just google something. The shuttle arrives at around 12:30 on Tuesdays so I can meet you at one easily...
Does the train continue to paoli station ? There is a starbucks right there.
Train arrives in paoli at 1:01!!! And I will have time to transfer.
